<h1 id="06-googleintegratedsystemconky">06. <a href="https://www.gnome-look.org/p/1206862/">GoogleIntegratedSystemConky</a></h1>
<p>The graphic elements and a general user interface are very bold and beautiful. The main aspect of this theme is the integration of some Google services. It can show upcoming events on your Google Calendar. You can also manage your to-do list created with another popular Google Keep app with this theme right on your desktop.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/img/conky/google-integrated-system.jpg" alt="GoogleIntegratedSystemConky" /></p>

<p><a href="https://www.gnome-look.org/p/1206862/" class="btn btn-success btn-lg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"> Get GoogleIntegratedSystemConky &lt;/ a&gt;</a></p>

