<h1 id="07-hightech-conky">07. <a href="https://www.gnome-look.org/p/1220192/">Hightech Conky</a></h1>
<p>This theme uses many visual elements and icons to give a completely futuristic look. Some of you may find it to be a somewhat complex setup. But you can configure it according to your needs and make some spaces.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/img/conky/hightech-conky-1.jpg" alt="Hightech Conky" /></p>

