<h1 id="08-conky-grapes">08. <a href="https://www.gnome-look.org/p/1296257/">Conky Grapes</a></h1>
<p>Setting it up with a clear desktop background and clear theme brings a comforting look to your Linux machine. This theme will show all parameters and relevant in dynamic rings.</p>

