<h1 id="09-conky-calendar">09. <a href="https://www.gnome-look.org/p/1115067/">Conky Calendar</a></h1>
<p>This is a useful Conky theme with a simple desktop calendar. There are different other themes available that can show the time and date. But those who want to see a full day view of the calendar will love this Conky. It was a personal project from the developer to his friend. Later, however, he gained a lot of popularity and he uploaded it for public use.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/img/conky/conky-calendar.jpg" alt="Conky Calendar" /></p>

<p><a href="https://www.gnome-look.org/p/1115067/" class="btn btn-success btn-lg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"> Get the Conky Calendar </a></p>

<h1 id="10-revolutionary-watch">10. <a href="https://www.gnome-look.org/p/1006556/">Revolutionary watch</a></h1>
<p>This is another watch for Conky. It will show the current time and date on a chronograph-style watch. There are several other small clocks within the larger one to show CPU usage, memory status and storage capacity. This Conky has a minimalist design that looks very clean and elegant.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/img/conky/revolutionary-clock-1.jpg" alt="Conky Revolutionary" /></p>

<p><a href="https://www.gnome-look.org/p/1006556/" class="btn btn-success btn-lg" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"> Get the Conky Revolutionary </a></p>

<hr />

<h1 id="11-victor-conky">11. <a href="https://www.gnome-look.org/p/1287775/">Victor Conky</a></h1>
<p>If you are designed to see the same old rounded user interface for most Conky themes, then this theme should be in your favor. Victor Conky has unconventional hexagonal visual elements. It features some powerful widgets for displaying computer statistics. This theme shows the time, date, processor load, memory usage and so on.</p>

