<h1 id="12-sci-fi-hud">12. <a href="https://www.gnome-look.org/p/1197920/">Sci-Fi HUD</a></h1>
<p>This Conky for Linux theme resembles an aircraftâ€™s Heads Up Display or HUD. The visual elements have a futuristic appearance painted on them. Perhaps these aspects have led the developer to name it so. Anyway, the theme has a little complexity in the user interface. But the general configuration is very polished. Thatâ€™s why it has become one of the most beautiful themes available for configuring your Conky.</p>

